    BRCAPRO

    BRCAPRO.Rd

    Runs PanelPRO with genes = c("BRCA1", "BRCA2") and cancers = c("Breast", "Ovarian", "Contralateral"), as in PanelPRO:::MODELPARAMS$BRCAPRO.

    BRCAPRO(...)

    Arguments

    ...

    Additional arguments to be passed into PanelPRO.

    See also

    PanelPRO

    Other predefined: BRCAPRO5(), BRCAPRO6(), MMRPRO(), PanelPRO11(), PanelPRO22()

    Examples

    data(test_fam_1)
BRCAPRO(test_fam_1, parallel = FALSE)
